p耐啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T22:54:01.000Z","msg":"台灣烘焙真係一流，路邊連鎖店已經好好食，<br />\n但加化學野呢點就睇你個人信唔信"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T23:12:44.000Z","msg":"唔多唔少都總有啲架啦，不過無所謂啦，又唔係日日食。最中意食查里布朗既芋頭流淚蛋糕，可惜無再出，食唔返"},{"pid":"cb86f9b553fdb70d542920a2de58e26f06975025","tid":509522,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T23:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早排去台灣幫人帶幾包黑糖珍珠（急凍）返黎</blockquote><br />\n依啲直接同人講過唔到境算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4fbbb39913fd110f3ccdf539940080ec315737","tid":509522,"uid":8203,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T23:51:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">屌你我老母要我係日本買鹽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"0d93668b9541fb351bd5c35184dfde4a6311c3e2","tid":509522,"uid":4824,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T23:56:22.000Z","msg":"我媽去韓國搬個西瓜返香港<br />\n利申：西瓜是我搬的"},{"pid":"186b27930a71b51b26ddd505d3826343a0b5912f","tid":509522,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T00:14:58.000Z","msg":"啱食咪食<br />\n唔啱食咪由佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢帶啫又唔係要你幫手帶<br />\n人哋帶咩返嚟食都要理咩"},{"pid":"7dbcea3bcc10c919fed67ea9094575c9cafad8b0","tid":509522,"uid":139243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T01:14:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3a36dc9f1e34c408a295734e7555e176249ed397","tid":509522,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:13:44.000Z","msg":"見過有人去台北寄把地拖入倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1909333f92f017da953dd47b72086f9476b0b4","tid":509522,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37fe01842ad96498277b660a9d7c9d2e4d296f3d","tid":509522,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T19:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>經修訂的《進口野味、肉類、家禽及蛋類規例》於2015年12月5日起生效，任何人把禽蛋輸入本港，必須持有食環署署長認可的來源地發證單位所發出的衞生證明書，證明有關禽蛋適宜供人食用。<br />\n<br />\n帶蛋返香港其實犯法，除非全熟&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>咁所有台灣返來嘅旅客應該要全部檢查有冇帶溫泉強先得嘞  &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/offtopic.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>唔能是掛&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote>的確係，只係平時過海關無查你&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n七仔溫泉蛋咪已經全熟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:18:56.000Z","msg":"全熟就唔叫温泉蛋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d7bdc25a350d2035ea75dd209a895fdad071ad8","tid":509522,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前條仔試過帶左幾個士林夜市啲生煎包返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識食<br />\n台灣人落甜/辣醬<br />\n我乜都唔落香港口味<br />\n<br />\n好食過香港d早餐舖整果d <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adb6ccbc26ed19713999bf580b1c67e57f02178","tid":509522,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實台灣啲麵包真係好食過香港多多聲，是但搵間都可以媲美香港啲高級麵包店。我阿媽每次去都拎3、4條麵包返黎做早餐，放冰箱可以keep耐啲</blockquote>台灣烘焙真係一流，路邊連鎖店已經好好食，<br />\n但加化學野呢點就睇你個人信唔信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得細舖未必有<br />\n純粹覺得<br />\n<br />\n不過台灣蒜蓉包真係唔錯<br />\n成件痴滿蒜蓉又多蔥又軟<br />\n<br />\n你睇下pizza 乞果塊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238d59d39c8c114662613e1f69cc04ab013dc7c1","tid":509522,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>帶洪瑞珍<br />\n<em>點睇</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我老母係帶全聯嗰啲方包<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食落有咩分別？<br />\n會唔會佢有另一番體會你冇去了解？<br />\n<br />\n利申未試過買返香港<br />\n民宿/酒店現場食就唔覺有咩分別</blockquote>佢食都未食過，只係覺得好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次最後一日行程試下其他包啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c9a98c7a8e4cf7a8c3eddc88265e6dd54f8e53","tid":509522,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過有人去台北寄把地拖入倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好難明白"},{"pid":"d75173852d71dbed58c398b332507db2e8c3337e","tid":509522,"uid":22374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"238d59d39c8c114662613e1f69cc04ab013dc7c1","tid":509522,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>帶洪瑞珍<br />\n<em>點睇</em><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我老母係帶全聯嗰啲方包<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食落有咩分別？<br />\n會唔會佢有另一番體會你冇去了解？<br />\n<br />\n利申未試過買返香港<br />\n民宿/酒店現場食就唔覺有咩分別</blockquote>佢食都未食過，只係覺得好平<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次最後一日行程試下其他包啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"有帶佢去啲高級麵包店,但佢唔買,係都要買全聯嗰啲方包<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35783f6f0940bf106ea5fc6fea8edbfc61071d1","tid":509522,"uid":5149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-26T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"帶拎住方包既老母番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}